I have seen the allega- tions that have been made with regard to the nationalities of the people of that dis- trict and have taken the trouble to go into that question. Any one who is acquainted with the circumstances out there will know that the people are not absolutely divided by division wa’lls into different nationalities or classes or religions. Now, in. regard to the character of the people. The city of Edmonton cast a total of 1,343 'votes. The city of Edmonton is admitted to be if not the most rapidll‘ly progressing place in this Dominion, at least one of the most progres- sive.
